responses: {"Q0":"Jason has cancer, and needs expensive medical treatment to battle it. He is in a lot of pain."}

{"Q0":"The psychology of people to be willing to donate \"free money.\" There are many thousands of people suffering from cancer, and donating to all of them would be outside of almost everyone's budget. But hearing a story of one person's suffering can make someone sympathetic and willing to donate to that person.
